      <title>Planned Danish skyscraper will be tallest in western Europe</title>
      <description><![CDATA[For story suggestions or custom animation requests, contact tips@nextanimation.com.tw. Visit http://archive.nextanimationstudio.com to view News Direct's complete archive of 3D news animations.RESTRICTIONS: Broadcast: NO USE JAPAN, NO USE TAIWAN Digital: NO USE JAPAN, NO USE TAIWANThe Danish town of Brande [e] is to get a brand new skyscraper designed by architectural firm Dorte Mandrup[f][g][h], reports the Guardian.The project is being helmed by Bestseller, a fashion brand that was founded in the town of Brande.The Tower and Village skyscraper in Denmark will be the tallest building in western Europe once it is complete, The Guardian reports.The 320-meter skyscraper will be taller than London's Shard skyscraper by 10.4 meters. That building is currently western Europe's tallest building.The building will oversee the town, providing a view of the countryside.At the base of the skyscraper, low to mid rise buildings with green roofs will also be included. In a news release from Bestseller, the project's manager Anders Krogh said the skyscraper would "place Brande on the map."He added that the building would also serve as an architectural attraction.  RUNDOWN SHOWS:1. The skyscraper2. The Danish skyscraper versus London's Shard skyscraper3. View of the countryside4. Base of the skyscraper with low to mid rise buildingsVOICEOVER (in English): "The Guardian reports the Tower and Village skyscraper in Denmark will be the tallest building in western Europe once it is complete.""The 320-meter skyscraper will be taller than London's Shard skyscraper by 10.4 meters.""That building is currently western Europe's tallest building.""The tower will oversee the town, providing a view of the countryside.""At the base of the skyscraper, low to mid rise buildings with green roofs will also be included." SOURCES: The Guardian, The Copenhagen Post, The Washington Post, BESTSELLER, Dorte Mandruphttps://www.theguardian.com/cities/2019/apr/01/like-the-eye-of-sauron-western-europes-tallest-building-planned-for-tiny-danish-town-brande-bestsellerhttp://cphpost.dk/news/national/bestseller-tower-gets-green-light-to-be-the-same-height-as-the-eiffel-tower.htmlhttps://www.washingtonpost.com/world/2019/04/01/denmark-will-be-building-europes-tallest-skyscraper-town-could-this-be-new-trend/?noredirect=on&utm_term=.6bc8e18b588ehttps://about.bestseller.com/news/plans-approved-still-a-long-way-to-gohttps://www.dortemandrup.dk/work/tower-village***]]></description>
