e. "When the Astrobees' batteries begin to run low, they will automatically fly to a docking system in the ISS to recharge."SOURCES: NASA, Digital Trendshttps://www.nasa.gov/astrobeehttps://www.digitaltrends.com/cool-tech/space-station-to-take-delivery-of-flying-astrobee-robots/***]]></description>
